        <a href="https://www.yosemiteconservancy.org/blog/sequoia-science">
         story
        </a>
        featuring Yazmin Lommel related to our collaboration with Yosemite National Park to better understand the giant sequoia seedling niche.
       </p>
       <p>
        Some of us will be attending/presenting research at the
        <a href="http://www.exploresequoiakingscanyon.com/science-symposium.html">
         Sequoia and Kings Canyon Science Symposium
        </a>
        . Hope to see you there.
       </p>
       <p>
        We enjoyed a few weeks of writing and analysis fun with Visiting Scientist,
